a.text: Pick up and wash the old blanket
Fix watering can and place it
Cut table into pieces and carry it away
Grow a fly trap and feed it
Remove lid and place a barrel
Kill the ivy and remove it
Clean up the shelf with chemicals
Dust off books and place them
Wash plush toy and place it
Sprinkle rose leaves on the floor
Sprinkle rose petals on the floor
Wash rug in flowery scent and place it
Replace the fountain center and clean it
